    "headline": "Akamai (AKAM) Q1 2026 Earnings Transcript",
    "summary": "In just a few months, we have achieved major milestones for our cloud computing strategy, marking a definitive turning point in the growth and evolution of our business.  Akamai has long been known for operating the world's largest distributed platform for delivery and security solutions at global scale, with a reputation for reliability, quality, and trust.  By integrating NVIDIA AI infrastructure into Akamai's massive distributed platform and by leveraging intelligent workload orchestration across our network, we intend to move the market for AI beyond isolated AI factories toward a unified distributed grid for AI inference.",
